		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Historicity of Jesus</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about the evidence regarding Jesus' existence.  For skeptical views, see <a href="/wiki/Christ_myth_theory" title="Christ myth theory">Christ myth theory</a>.  For historical reconstructions of Jesus, see <a href="/wiki/Historical_Jesus" title="Historical Jesus">Historical Jesus</a>.</div>
