<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> Brown 7</li>
<li id="cite_note-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12" title="">^</a></b> For an early date, see: J. A. T. Robinson, <i>Redating the New Testament</i>, and William F. Albright, <i>Towards a More Conservative View</i>, in Christianity Today (18 January 1963); for a late date, see R. Bultmann, <i>Kerygma and Myth: A Theological Debate</i>; for a brief overview, see also <a href="http://www.bethinking.org/resource.php?ID=233" class="external text" title="http://www.bethinking.org/resource.php?ID=233" rel="nofollow">this article</a> at bethinking.org</li>
